Maharaja (2023)
Maharaja completes 1 year today! Directed by Nithilan Swaminathan, this Tamil thriller starred Makkal Selvan Vijay Sethupathi in a powerful, emotionally layered role as a humble barber whose calm demeanor hides a storm of vengeance. The gripping story revolves around his mysterious complaint to the police about his stolen “Lakshmi” — a seemingly simple case that unfolds into a dark, intense journey of justice and retribution. With standout performances by Anurag Kashyap, Mamta Mohandas, and Abhirami, the film left fans stunned with its unexpected twists and brilliant climax. One year later, Maharaja still stands tall as one of Tamil cinema’s finest revenge thrillers. 🎬🔥

latestPosts.caption:
5 years ♥️🥹 

Can’t believe it’s been five years since Choked. Some films give you more than just a role, they give you a piece of your life. Choked was that for me. It was one of the most creatively and emotionally fulfilling experiences I’ve had… and what made it truly unforgettable was the people. I found lifelong friends. @anuragkashyap10 and @roshan.matthew even now, are my first go - to people.

Rakyesh sir with Mirzya, Anurag with choked and Balki sir with ghoomer spoilt me and pampered me and I keep longing to be on a set like theirs. Manifesting these sets soon! 

Grateful for the story. Grateful for the people. Grateful for the journey. ❤️

@misterbistar @sylvesterfonseca @amrutasubhash @rajshri_deshpande @upendralimaye @zoparvin @prashant316 @malikakumar @animeshpanwar @mongashivang @shubhrashetty
